Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.83,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Good afternoon. It's nice to meet you.}Xin chào, rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.37,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{We're gods!}Thần linh đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:25.46,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{Don't be ridiculous! Do you realize\N who you're talking to?!}Đừng có giỡn mặt! Các ngươi nghĩ \Nmình đang nói chuyện với ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:29.84,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{I am the one true holy arbiter of the \NDivine Prontea who once blessed this land!}Ta là giáo hoàng đã được ngài Prontea ban phước.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:34.05,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{I am the Third Holy Pontiff \Nof Sarabael, Sagishi Sakushu!}Đức giáo hàng III của Sarabael, Sagishi Sakushu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:36.63,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{"The Divine Prontea"?}Thần Prontea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:39.39,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Well, let's just say this \Ncountry has its own backstory.}Nhiều chuyện xảy ra lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:44.56,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Okay then. Stick to the plan, \Nall right, Paula?}Vậy theo kế hoạch nhé Paula?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:45.90,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Right.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:52.06,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{How's that?! Behold the righteous wrath\N of God's divine punishment!}Thế nào hả? Hãy run sợ trước \Nsự tức giận của thần linh đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:56.13,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{Another unclean soul has \Nbeen delivered unto salv...}Lại một linh hồn ô uế đã được về với...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:05.64,Flashback,Paula,0,0,0,,{Is this good enough? But I can't \Nfly with them or anything.}Vậy ổn chứ? Nhưng tớ không bay được đâu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.20,Flashback,Paula,0,0,0,,{They're just for decoration.}Chúng chỉ để trang trí thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:08.49,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{That should suffice.}Vậy được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.96,Flashback,Paula,0,0,0,,{So, what now?}Vậy giờ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:12.80,Flashback,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Just make something up.}Làm gì tùy cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.40,Italics,Paula,0,0,0,,{That isn't very helpful...}Làm gì bây giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:19.73,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Uh, I came here today to talk with you all.}À, tôi đến đây có chuyện muốn nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.56,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{What are you all doing?! \NDon't let her tricks fool you!}Các ngươi làm gì thế hả? Đừng để bị lừa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.61,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{Those wings are fake! It's just a costume!}Đôi cánh đó chỉ là đồ trang trí! Là đồ giả!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:29.00,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{T-Technically, yes...}Ừ thì đúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.94,Main,Sagishi,0,0,0,,{Taste the lord's might!}Nhận lấy! Sự trừng phạt của thần linh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:40.40,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{This is gonna be rough. \NThey aren't listening at all—}Phiền thật. Họ chẳng chịu nghe mình...
