Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.34,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Is this gonna work?}Tìm ra được không đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.66,Main,Beefy guys,0,0,0,,{You're not going any farther!}Đừng hòng tiến vào nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.83,Main,Beefy guys,0,0,0,,{We're gonna show you the \Npower of the Super Beefy Bros.!}Bọn ta sẽ cho các ngươi thấy sức mạnh\N của anh em nhà cơ bắp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.64,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{Oh? Hayato's grown a lot stronger.}Hayato có vẻ mạnh hơn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.03,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{This is gonna take all damn day.}Mất thời gian quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.48,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Let's split up, Granny.}Chia ra đi bà già.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.49,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{He's still not quite as \Nreliable as Prontea, but...}Vẫn chưa đáng tin tưởng bằng Prontea nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.08,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{I'm pretty sure I pierced that one's heart.}Mình nghĩ đã đâm thủng tim rồi chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.64,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{Did I miss?}Hụt à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.45,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{What's with them? \NThey're suddenly moving much sharper.}Chúng bị sao thế? Tự nhiên di chuyển nhanh hơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.27,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.72,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Can't move with their heads gone.}Cắt đầu là hết di chuyển à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.85,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{They're still not dead, \Neven after losing their heads?!}Vẫn chưa chết dù mất đầu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.61,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Wh-What is this?}C-Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.09,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{She's so solid!}Cứng quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:40.17,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{I won't be able to keep her away \Nwith ultra-thin hair alone....}Mình không thể giữ ả ta chỉ với mớ tóc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:41.61,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Still, I must remain calm.}Nhưng phải bình tĩnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.76,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{She's not the kind of enemy\N I can beat head-on.}Ả ta là đối thủ không nên đánh trực diện.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.26,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{The important thing is that she \Nassumes she's fighting weaklings.}Cho ả ta chiến với lũ lót đường.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.85,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{I need her to believe that.}Phải dụ ả vào tròng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:55.96,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,{The hell is that?}Cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.58,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,{One of General Piscalat's men?}Người của chỉ huy Piscalat à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.85,Main,Troops,0,0,0,,{Keep firing! Shoot him down!}Bắn đi! Bắn chết nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.14,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You're a demon, aren't you?}Ngươi là quỷ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:12.14,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Hey, get your ass back here!}Này, đứng lại đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.42,Main,Prisoners,0,0,0,,{I can't take it anymore!}Chịu hết nởi rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.97,Main,Prisoners,0,0,0,,{Let us out of here!}Thả tôi ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.45,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Everyone, you mustn't lose hope!}Mọi người, đừng từ bỏ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.99,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I'm sure God will show us mercy!}Chúa sẽ cứu rỗi chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.37,Main,Prisoners,0,0,0,,{Hey, over there!}Bên kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.42,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Man, he managed to get pretty far...}Thiệt tình, chạy gì xa thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.89,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Huh, why didn't those humans run?}Ủa? Sao không chạy đi, con người?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.95,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Wh-Who are you?}C-Cậu là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:42.55,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{No, it doesn't matter right now.\NPlease, help us!}Không, không quan trọng. Xin hãy cứu chúng tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.87,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Open these cells!}Hãy mở song sắt này ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:47.24,Main,Prisoners,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Please! Help!}Làm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:49.43,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Cells? Huh, so this is how \Nyou keep humans in place...}Song sắt? À, không ra được hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:59.16,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Well, you're free, but you might \Nbe safer staying in here for now.}Rồi đó. Nhưng mấy cô nên ở trong đó cho an toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:02.67,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Though it all depends on how \Nwild the crazy old bitch gets...}Mà còn tùy vào bà già điên kia nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.81,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{J-Just who are you...?}C-cậu là ai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.52,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{He's a god.}Là thần linh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:13.41,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Albeit not the kind of all-powerful \Ncreator deity that you worship.}Dù không phải loại thần toàn năng mà cô tôn thờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.17,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{E-Emperor Takeshita?!}B-Bệ hạ Takeshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.51,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{You all have won this war.}Lần này các ngươi đã thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:23.87,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{But for the sake of the future... \NI need to at least manage to kill you.}Nhưng vì tương lai... ta sẽ giết chết ngươi.
